4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for those seeking to become cybersecurity specialists, regardless of prior knowledge. The program lasts 16 weeks, featuring 3 live online classes weekly with a maximum of 16 students per class. Participants will gain foundational skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, while mastering cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. The bootcamp also emphasizes data loss prevention and compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Upon completion, students receive an official certificate recognized by multiple institutions. The course is available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop